title: Output parameter should be displayed in data set dialog
description: Currently, when calling a stored procedure from an Oracle database, the query result is stored in an output parameter as an object. However, this output parameter is not being displayed in the edit data set dialog.
OB: The output parameter is not displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce this issue:
1. Call a stored procedure from an Oracle database.
2. Check the edit data set dialog to see if the output parameter is displayed.
